de.esoco.ewt.impl.gwt

Interface WidgetFactory<W extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.IsWidget>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Button.ButtonWidgetFactory, Calendar.CalendarWidgetFactory, CheckBox.CheckBoxWidgetFactory, ComboBox.ComboBoxWidgetFactory, DateField.DateFieldWidgetFactory, FileChooser.FileChooserWidgetFactory, Label.LabelWidgetFactory, ListControl.ListControlWidgetFactory, ProgressBar.ProgressBarWidgetFactory, RadioButton.RadioButtonWidgetFactory, Spinner.SpinnerWidgetFactory, TableControl.TableControlWidgetFactory, TextArea.TextAreaWidgetFactory, TextField.TextFieldWidgetFactory, ToggleButton.ToggleButtonWidgetFactory, Tree.TreeWidgetFactory, Website.WebsiteWidgetFactory

    public interface WidgetFactory<W extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.IsWidget>
    The interface for factories that produce widget instances for a certain GEWT component type. Implementations of the interface method can either return subclasses of Widget or some kind of widget wrapper that implements the interface IsWidget. The latter can be used to implement additional interfaces that are not directly available in the wrapped widget. The needed interfaces are documented in the GWT widget factories of the original GEWT components which should typically be subclassed by new factories.
